'''Aqua-skimmers''' were submersible vehicles used by the [[Aquaris Freeholders/Legends|Aquaris Freeholders]] for underwater use. The [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] would sometimes use their aqua-skimmers for hunting expeditions.

